Definition: the right to buy or sell property at an agreed price
Example: the right is purchased and if it is not exercised by a stated date the money is forfeited
Synonyms: noun, communication, derivative_instrument, the, right, to, buy, or, sell, property, at, an, agreed, price, is, purchased, and, if, it, not, exercised, by, a, stated, date, money, forfeited
Category: noun.possession
